Format de l'url :
http://www.t411.me/torrents/search/?name=$(NAME)&description=&file=&user=&cat=210&subcat=$(CATEGORY)&term%5B46%5D%5B%5D=$(EPISODE)&term%5B45%5D%5B%5D=$(SEASON)&term%5B17%5D%5B%5D=($LANGAGE)&search=%40name+$(NAME)+&submit=Recherche

